        <p>I'm a Bitcoin Maximalist, putting in my few thousand hours since 2017. I have a degree in Economics and Business from Trinity College Dublin, and an MBA from the Kellogg School of Management at Northwestern University. I've spent 25 years working in Product Management in Silicon Valley, including long stints at Yahoo and Mastercard - the latter focused specifically on merchant loyalty, an expertise I've since turned toward Bitcoin.</p>
